---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';
const pageTitle = "Products & Services";
---

<style>

</style>

<MainLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>

    <!-- Product 1: SPA/PWA Development -->
    <article id="spa-pwa-development">
        <h3>Single Page Applications (SPA) & Progressive Web Applications (PWA) Development</h3>
        <p>I specialize in developing modern Single Page Applications (SPA) and Progressive Web Applications (PWA) using
            JavaScript. My expertise includes building browser-based, serverless applications and integrating them with
            various external services, such as payment gateways, large language models (LLM), and other APIs. This
            allows businesses to extend their online capabilities and provide seamless user experiences.</p>
        <p>In addition to development, I offer full deployment services, ensuring that your application is set up on a
            virtual host or cloud infrastructure. I also provide Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment
            (CI/CD) pipelines using GitHub Actions, which ensures efficient and reliable updates throughout the
            application’s lifecycle.</p>
        <p>Whether you need a new custom web app or want to modernize an existing one, I will work closely with you to
            deliver a solution that meets your business objectives.</p>
    </article>

    <!-- Product 2: Telegram Bot Development -->
    <article id="telegram-bot-development">
        <h3>Custom Telegram Bot Development</h3>
        <p>I offer the development of fully customizable Telegram bots using Node.js and the grammY library. These bots
            can be tailored to meet specific business needs, whether for customer service, automation, or content
            delivery. My solutions are designed for easy deployment and maintenance, giving you the flexibility to
            expand bot functionalities as your needs evolve.</p>
        <p>Bots can be deployed in long polling or webhook mode, depending on your preference. I also offer hosting
            solutions on my own virtual server, ensuring your bot is securely hosted and maintained. For long-term
            reliability, I can assist with integration, scaling, and optimizing performance.</p>
        <p>This service is ideal for businesses looking to enhance their customer engagement on Telegram with an
            intelligent, responsive bot that can be easily adapted over time.</p>
    </article>

    <!-- Product 3: Tequila Framework -->
    <article id="tequila-framework">
        <h3>Tequila Framework: Custom Web & Node.js Application Development</h3>
        <p>The Tequila Framework is a custom platform I developed to create web and Node.js applications with ease.
            Using pure JavaScript and a modular monolithic architecture, it provides a robust foundation for building
            scalable and maintainable applications. The key feature of the framework is its ability to reuse code across
            both frontend and backend, simplifying the development process and reducing maintenance costs.</p>
        <p>Tequila Framework supports seamless integration with various external services, such as authentication
            systems, payment gateways, and large language models (LLMs). This flexibility allows businesses to develop
            complex applications that can scale as needed, without sacrificing performance or reliability.</p>
        <p>This platform is suitable for clients who want custom-built solutions for web or mobile applications and need
            a foundation that can grow alongside their business requirements.</p>
    </article>

</MainLayout>